stories.title: Roaring to life
stories.subTitle: India v New Zealand, Videocon Cup, Harare
stories.summary: With no Shane Bond to take the shine off the white lacquer, India's batsmen could express themselves without a hint of trepidation
stories.byline: The Wisden Verdict by Dileep Premachandran

stories.title: Cairns ruled out of Videocon Cup final
stories.subTitle: New Zealand's injury worries
stories.summary: Chris Cairns, the New Zealand allrounder, has been ruled out of the rest of the Videocon Cup in Zimbabwe owing to a recurrence of a hamstring injury

stories.title: Kaif stars in India's run chase
stories.subTitle: India v New Zealand, Videocon Tri-Series, Harare
stories.summary: A superbly paced 102 not out by Mohammad Kaif helped India to a six-wicket win against New Zealand
